Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.47,0:00:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, turn your sadness into kindness,\Nyour uniqueness into strength
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.80,0:00:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you get lost, let’s start walking
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.14,0:00:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more time
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.14,0:00:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really happy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.93,0:00:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when you're always meeting\Nto someone's expectations?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.64,0:00:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you change to\Nwho you really wanna be
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.55,0:00:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you always have a great smile?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.85,0:00:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dreaming of only “the beginning,”\NI wake up
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.47,0:00:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and someday, I'll live on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.72,0:01:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, precious things are never in shape
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.89,0:01:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You never know what it is\Nwhen you get it or lose it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.84,0:01:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, turn your sadness into kindness,\Nyour uniqueness into strength
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.22,0:01:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you get lost,\Nlet's start walking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.84,0:01:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more time
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.84,0:01:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.84,0:01:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was worth teaching you Genjutsu\Nin survival training
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.64,0:01:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,during the Genin Exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.26,0:01:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You truly have a talent for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.60,0:01:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.22,0:01:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Release the Genjutsu and\Nwake up Naruto and Shikamaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.18,0:02:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto will be delighted.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.47,0:02:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He’ll be getting a mission\Nafter such a long while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.30,0:02:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by a mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.18,0:02:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.10,0:02:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s the first A-Ranked mission\Nsince the Land of the Waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.43,0:02:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Village in Distress:\NA New A-Ranked Mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.35,0:02:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei! What do you mean by A-Ranked\Nmission in the condition we are in?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.84,0:02:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we have to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.47,0:02:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasuke is chasing Gaara and company\Nof the Sand Village.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.72,0:02:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.05,0:02:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Release the Genjutsu\Non Naruto and Shikamaru,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.18,0:02:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and go after Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.85,0:02:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel uneasy…\Nabout that unusual Chakra.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.14,0:02:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.68,0:03:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we should wake up Ino and Choji\Nand go in a large group.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.60,0:03:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There may already\Nbe quite a large number
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.30,0:03:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of Sand and Sound Shinobi\Nwho have infiltrated this village.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.05,0:03:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actions lose quickness when there’s more\Nthan the fundamental four in a squad…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.26,0:03:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and it becomes difficult to\Nhide from the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.84,0:03:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You learned that in the Academy's\Npatrol practical training, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.05,0:03:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see! Then four means\Nthat you’ll come with us…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.84,0:03:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I must not leave here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.51,0:03:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summoning Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.84,0:03:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As for the rest, this Pakkun will\Ntrack down Sasuke by scent!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.10,0:03:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Could it be…\Nthe one other member is this puppy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.26,0:03:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Little girl!\NDon’t you be calling me a cute puppy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.55,0:03:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn’t say…cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.80,0:04:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Sakura! Release the Genjutsu\Non Naruto and Shikamaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.93,0:04:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.43,0:04:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Release!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.84,0:04:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it…Sakura?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.84,0:04:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.14,0:04:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll tell you later!\NJust stay down!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.35,0:04:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shikamaru…you were…\Nfrom the beginning…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.64,0:04:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Owwee!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.76,0:04:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were able to release Genjutsu, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.30,0:05:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why were you pretending\Nto be asleep?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.68,0:05:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humph! I don’t want to\Nend up getting involved!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.84,0:05:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heck no…\NI could care less about Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.80,0:05:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Owwee!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.01,0:05:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's going on…?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.84,0:05:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto! Behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.47,0:05:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,F-Fast…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.84,0:05:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not just fast…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.01,0:05:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guy Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.76,0:05:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I’ll announce the mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.84,0:05:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as you’ve heard what\Nthe mission is, go through that hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.05,0:05:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Track down Sasuke,\Njoin up and then stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.26,0:05:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then await next orders\Nin a safe place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.76,0:06:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Did something happen\Nto Sasuke?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.76,0:06:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll tell you the reason en route!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.10,0:06:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.84,0:06:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez… Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.18,0:06:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.80,0:06:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh…?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.68,0:06:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this mission is a success,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.84,0:06:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as a reward I’ll let you\Ntouch my paw-pads.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.93,0:06:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So don’t sulk like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.84,0:06:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.84,0:06:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.68,0:06:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They’re soft and supple!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.39,0:06:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Su..pple…?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.55,0:06:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, very…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.55,0:06:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soft and Supple!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.72,0:06:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s just go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.93,0:06:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.72,0:06:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will it be okay with just them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.01,0:06:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They’ll be okay.\NPakkun is with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.39,0:06:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as they don’t pursue too far…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.68,0:07:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think I’d be able to fight you again…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.97,0:07:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This barrier can’t be broken\Nunless it’s from the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.64,0:07:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Lord Hokage would just\Ntake out one of those four,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.18,0:07:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we could help…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.64,0:07:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it’s gonna start soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.84,0:07:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put up a barrier on the inside, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.68,0:07:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.10,0:07:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm… It doesn’t look like\NI’ll be able to get out this easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.01,0:08:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don’t really mean that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.10,0:08:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’d be tougher for you if someone\Ncame in and got in the way, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.84,0:08:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ninja Art: Tile Shuriken!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.60,0:08:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s too easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.84,0:08:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Striking Shadow Snake!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.14,0:08:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With such a weak technique…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.84,0:08:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sucks to get old, eh,\NSarutobi Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.80,0:08:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Substitution?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.35,0:08:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Earth Style: Great Mud River!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.84,0:09:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.35,0:09:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t think so!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.80,0:09:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Earth Style: Earth Dragon Bomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.10,0:09:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire Dragon Bomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.68,0:09:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s combined Earth and Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.01,0:09:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent, Lord Hokage!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.97,0:09:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop the stupid act, Orochimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.76,0:09:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very good…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.97,0:09:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, I’ve been grossly underestimated.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.84,0:09:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think you could kill me\Nwith that level of Jutsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.80,0:09:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humph… A hateful fellow as usual!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.22,0:09:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.84,0:10:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A high maintenance student is cute.\NRight, Sarutobi Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.84,0:10:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something’s strange…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.14,0:10:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of the Academy’s classes\Ndoing self-study.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.60,0:10:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that smoke…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.10,0:10:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's coming from the direction\Nof the exam arena.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.47,0:10:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there some disturbance\Nto the east?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.80,0:10:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if something happened…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.26,0:10:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is definitely strange!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.39,0:10:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But sudden self-study is\Nsure a smack in the eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.47,0:10:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s been like this for a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.51,0:10:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Iruka Sensei\Nand everyone are late…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.43,0:11:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren’t they, Konohamaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.14,0:11:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Konohamaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.35,0:11:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.22,0:11:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, what is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.47,0:11:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Mom just bought this for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.39,0:11:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll loan you my colored pencil.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.68,0:11:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’re you saying?!\NThis color is this spring’s new color!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.84,0:11:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aww, what'll I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.85,0:11:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is…?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.35,0:11:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Naruto and the others\Nwent to stop Sasuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.84,0:11:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those brats?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.51,0:11:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But surely, some Genin won’t\Nbe able to make any difference…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.01,0:12:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Is this the data of\Nthat kid back there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.39,0:12:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You give him too much credit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.18,0:12:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.39,0:12:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’ll trip up if you underestimate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.89,0:12:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Teachers' Office
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.14,0:12:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is information that several units\Nhave already infiltrated the village…!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.97,0:12:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should evacuate the students\Nto a safe place right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.30,0:12:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes… And without causing panic\Namong the students!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.26,0:12:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let’s evacuate the students
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.84,0:13:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as soon as possible under\Nthe pretense of an evacuation drill!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.84,0:13:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn’t it about time\Nwe stopped playing around?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.43,0:13:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn’t an Academy class, so…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.76,0:13:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.10,0:13:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you foresee your final moments?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.43,0:14:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won’t go easy on you\Njust because you’re doddering.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.51,0:14:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I look forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.72,0:14:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Depending on your Jutsu,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.60,0:14:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I might have to have you\Nstart over at the Academy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.30,0:14:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don’t disappoint me too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.80,0:14:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wow…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.43,0:14:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What Chakra?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.43,0:14:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah… It seems the air is\Nbearing down within the body!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.51,0:14:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuriken Shadow Clone Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.47,0:15:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summoning Jutsu: Reanimation!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.84,0:15:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.64,0:15:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.84,0:15:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is using a Summoning Jutsu\Nas a shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.64,0:15:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this dead person is…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.26,0:15:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.60,0:15:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must stop the third one at any cost…!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.93,0:15:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.84,0:15:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like the third one was no good.\NOh well…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.51,0:15:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like I stopped the third one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.39,0:15:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, this is where it gets tough…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.76,0:15:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He summoned those two of all people…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.39,0:16:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It can’t be!\NThose personages are…!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.64,0:16:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those personages are?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.84,0:16:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, what will you do,\NSarutobi Sensei…?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.84,0:16:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.47,0:16:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord…Third Hokage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.18,0:16:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Everyone, please move quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.84,0:16:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what a day!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.18,0:16:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My favorite colored pencil\Ndidn’t have to break like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.14,0:16:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lousy evacuation drill…\NSelf-study was better.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.14,0:16:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Konohamaru’s been quiet, hasn’t he?\NI wonder what’s wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.14,0:16:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.60,0:17:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After the whole school does\Na long self-study,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.51,0:17:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the whole school does\Nan evacuation drill.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.51,0:17:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is too strange!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.47,0:17:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Stop! Get in line!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.84,0:17:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That look on Iruka Sensei’s face…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.93,0:17:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something’s definitely going on here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.84,0:17:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And also…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.26,0:17:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, everyone!\NDon’t go off on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.05,0:17:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That rainbow… It's been\Nbugging me for a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.05,0:17:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s that, Old Man?\NThere’s a strange rainbow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.85,0:17:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s an unusual rainbow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.10,0:18:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like rainbows, Konohamaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.84,0:18:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! And I’ve never seen\Nsuch a pretty rainbow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.47,0:18:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, I see.\NBut, Konohamaru…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.60,0:18:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.84,0:18:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rainbows used to symbolize snakes…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.51,0:18:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it’s said that they bode evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.84,0:18:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a pretty thing? That’s a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.84,0:18:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.35,0:18:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Symbolizes snakes…\Nls something happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.43,0:18:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see…Saru.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.26,0:19:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it’s you…\NYou’ve gotten old, Sarutobi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.14,0:19:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought I would meet\Nthe great brothers in this manner…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.89,0:19:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s regretful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.84,0:19:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.51,0:19:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Summoning Jutsu…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.80,0:19:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who in the world are they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.72,0:19:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please prepare yourselves…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.84,0:19:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord First Hokage…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.80,0:19:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Second Hokage!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.47,0:19:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s right…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.84,0:19:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one with the black hair\Nis the First Hokage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.18,0:19:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one with the white hair\Nis the Second Hokage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.84,0:19:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are both reputed to\Nbe the highest Shinobi
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.93,0:19:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they are the Hokages\Nwho built the today’s Leaf Village!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.85,0:19:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reanimation, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.26,0:19:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This youth summoned us with\Nthe Forbidden Jutsu, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.72,0:19:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s something else…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.89,0:19:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Sarutobi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.47,0:20:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does this mean we must…fight you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.60,0:20:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s stop the old people\Nget-together talk…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.84,0:20:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we get started?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.10,0:20:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s always fighting…\Nno matter when you live.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.84,0:20:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You like that, don’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.64,0:20:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No good will come by deriding the dead\Nand playing around with time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.84,0:20:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it! So that’s what happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.14,0:20:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Sasuke, getting all impatient!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.64,0:20:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, why am I pulled into this?!\NThis is such a drag!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.84,0:20:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can’t be helped!\Nlt’s Kakashi Sensei’s order.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.14,0:20:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.26,0:21:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That brat, huh…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.84,0:21:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.85,0:21:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone makes mistakes\Nlt’s nothing to be ashamed about
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.47,0:21:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t let this scar be for naught\NWalk with a smile
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.39,0:21:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, breathe in the air\NLift your face to the sky and jump
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.01,0:22:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it rains, take a break\NGo where the wind takes you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.43,0:22:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So many regrets\NDon’t let this scar be for naught
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.47,0:22:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s go carve the badges in our chest\NYes, it’s Show Time, life begins now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.72,0:22:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone makes mistakes\Nlt’s nothing to be ashamed about
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.05,0:22:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t let this scar be for naught\NWalk with a smile
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.68,0:22:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Transform sadness into the wind\Nand continue to forge on
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.22,0:22:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forge on strong
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.84,0:23:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it! The pursuer is too fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.85,0:23:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once we Genin get caught,\Nthat will be the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.51,0:23:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case,\Nwe should ambush and attack them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.84,0:23:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already thought of it,\Nbut it’ll probably be no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.89,0:23:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what should we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.18,0:23:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is only one choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.10,0:23:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, “A Shirker’s Call to Action:\NLayabout No More!”
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.97,0:23:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It isn’t my style,\Nbut we have no choice, I guess.
